2015;;The Legend of Barney Thomson;;British;;Director: Robert Carlyle;;Director: Robert CarlyleCast: Robert Carlyle, Emma Thompson, Ashley Jensen, Ray Winstone;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Barney_Thomson;;Set in Glasgow, the film centres around 50-year-old Barney Thomson, who works at Henderson's Barbers in Bridgeton and lives a life of desperate mediocrity. Barney's uninteresting life gets turned upside down when he enters the grotesque and comically absurd world of a serial killer after accidentally killing his boss Wullie.